{"lemma":"ساهِر","slug":"ساهِر","root":"س.ه.ر","root_slug":"س-ه-ر","root_link":"/words/roots/س-ه-ر","pos":"ADJ","pos_camel":"adj","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n21049"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B3%D8%A7%D9%87%D9%90%D8%B1"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to spend a sleepless night with","tags":["transitive"],"examples":[{"text":"سَاهَرَ أَحْمَدُ زَوْجَتَهُ","english":"Ahmad spent a sleepless night with his wife."},{"text":"سَاهَرَ النُجُومَ","english":"He passed the night sleepless like as do the stars."}]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/saː.ha.ra/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n21049","headword_ar":"سَاهِرٌ","root":"shr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sahoraAnN","text_ar":"سَهْرَانٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sah~aArN","text_ar":"سَهَّارٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suharapN","text_ar":"سُهَرَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) the last of which is an intensive epithet, (S,) [and so is the third, and sometimes the second,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Waking, sitting up, sleepless, wakeful,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"not sleeping, by night;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K;) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"abstaining from sleep by night;"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"remaining awake"},{"kind":"text","text":"all the night or a part thereof: (Msb:) and the last, [and third, and sometimes the second,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wakeful,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"waking much, &c."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlEayoni","text_ar":"العَيْنِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rajulN sah~aAru","text_ar":"رَجُلٌ سَهَّارُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A man whom sleep does not overcome."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lh.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baroqN saAhirN","text_ar":"بَرْقٌ سَاهِرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Lightning gleaming,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"glistening, during the night."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"layolN","text_ar":"لَيْلٌ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saAhri","text_ar":"سَاهرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A night of waking"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sleeplessness"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wakefulness:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) like as one says"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"layolN naAy^imN","text_ar":"لَيْلٌ نَايِمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saAhirapu AlEiroqi","text_ar":"سَاهِرَةُ العِرْقِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  A she-camel"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that yields milk long and abundantly."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EayonN saAhirapN","text_ar":"عَيْنٌ سَاهِرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A running spring"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fountain:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a spring"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fountain that runs night and day, unremittingly."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, * TA.) It is said in a trad.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xayoru AlmaAli EayonN saAhirapN","text_ar":"خَيْرُ المَالِ عَيْنٌ سَاهِرَةٌ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"liEayonK naAy^imapK","text_ar":"لِعَيْنٍ نَايِمَةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The best of property is a spring of water that runs night and day while its owner is sleeping;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA;) its owner having his mind unoccupied by it. (A.) ―         -b6-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aroDN saAhirapN","text_ar":"اَرْضٌ سَاهِرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Land that produces plants quickly:"},{"kind":"text","text":"as though it passed the night doing so. (A.) ―         -b7-  Also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saAhirapN","text_ar":"سَاهِرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[alone], (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A wide,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an extensive, tract of land, the traverser of which remains awake during the night:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"earth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"land:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"surface of the earth:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Fr, Lth, S, K:) because it produces plants or herbage alike by night and day: (Ibn-Es-Seed:) so in the Kur lxxix. 14: (S:) or (TA, but in the K “ and ”)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a desert,"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"falaApN","text_ar":"فَلَاةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the traverser of which remains awake during the night:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or (TA, but in the K “ and ”)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an untrodden land:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or (TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a land which God will create anew on the day of resurrection:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a land on which none has disobeyed God:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ibn-Es Seed:) or (TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Hell:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Katádeh, K:) or (TA) [in the Kur ubi suprà]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a certain mountain of Jerusalem:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Wahb Ibn-Munebbih, K:) or (TA) the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"land of Syria."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mukátil, K.)"}],"source_refs":["S","Msb","K","A","Fr","Lth","TA"]}]}}